  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Full 13-factor assessment completed; decision record records outcome as Accepted. Two credibility factors are recorded without requiredLevel or achievedLevel, introducing a factor-decision inconsistency (W-CON-01).",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-absolute-threshold",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cou2-vad-cfd-hemolysis",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-centrifugal-pump-hemolysis",
